    "description": "BLOCKGUN is a fast paced 3D Platformer speedrun oriented in which you have to infiltrate a computer system. But don't worry you have a block gun ! Use blocks to create platform to make a path to the end of each level and finish each level as quick as possible !<br><br><strong>The blockgun</strong><br><br>Thanks to your block gun you will be able to infiltrate the system. Depending on how long you charge your gun, you will shoot different projectile:<br><br>A short charging will shoot a simple bullet that allows you to trigger some interrupter and mechanisms: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/5b439526d6ab4f8feba9783350756250.poster.avif?t=1689171514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/5b439526d6ab4f8feba9783350756250.webm?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/5b439526d6ab4f8feba9783350756250.mp4?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A medium time charging will shoot a sticky platform allowing you to jump on it to reach the end of levels: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/b2fa4a6c6a7ff70870c58044e98ee45e.poster.avif?t=1689171514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/b2fa4a6c6a7ff70870c58044e98ee45e.webm?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/b2fa4a6c6a7ff70870c58044e98ee45e.mp4?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A long time charging will shoot a moving platform that will get destroyed after few seconds :<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/4edd3aee32c86c6387a3bcd212c89af5.poster.avif?t=1689171514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/4edd3aee32c86c6387a3bcd212c89af5.webm?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/4edd3aee32c86c6387a3bcd212c89af5.mp4?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But be careful, you have a limited amount of cubes in your gun, get back your old cubes or new ones before trying to create new platforms :<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/80a98420425ff2a8b1a6cb0917f54d84.poster.avif?t=1689171514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/80a98420425ff2a8b1a6cb0917f54d84.webm?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382410/extras/80a98420425ff2a8b1a6cb0917f54d84.mp4?t=1689171514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Speedrun oriented</strong><br><br>Each level has a gold medal time to beat, but it is only the beginning, then you can try to beat the developer time or even try to be the first in the global leaderboard.<br>You can also try to be first in the speedrun, where you need to finish all the levels without break, will you be able to finish the speedrun without any death ?",
